heisigStory: The strand referred to here is the stretch of land along a beach or shoreline. Its elements are: water . . . puppet.
koohiiStory1: I was stranded on a desert island surrounded by water for hundreds of miles on end. I wasn´t upset though - I had my love doll! What a great strand of sand to be stranded on - just me and my love doll!
koohiiStory2: A lovely romantic walk on the strand, splashing in the water with my love doll.
